primary.request: register for a new website account
primary.context: Customer received a message that their ownership type requires special handling for online registration.
primary.detail: The agent verified the customer's contract and sent a registration link for the Clubhouse portal to the email on file.

steps: Customer requested help with website registration.
Agent attempted lookup via phone number but failed.
Agent successfully located record using contract ID.
Agent verified identity using owner name and state of residence.
Agent confirmed contact details and sent the registration link via email.

clarifications.note: Agent clarifying if registration or password reset
Agent asking to spell name for accuracy

corrections.note: Customer clarifies multiple owners on contract

actions.detail: Lookup by Brazilian phone number failed
Verified name and state of residence
Sent registration link to Yahoo email

insights.summary: The customer needed help registering for the new website due to a 'special handling' error. The agent successfully verified the account using a contract ID and sent the necessary registration link.
insights.verbatim: Perfect. So I have to log in in Vacatia, the new website.
